ActSaguenay-St. Lawrence Marine Park Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Marine Activities in the Saguenay-St. Lawrence Marine Park Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the MARINE ACTIVITIES IN THE SAGUENAY-ST. LAWRENCE MARINE PARK REGULATIONS in order to (1) update the standards governing the management of the marine park and the activities carried out there; (2) respond to the recommendations of the Harmonization Committee and the Coordinating Commitee; and (3) respond to the recommendation of the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
